Opto Mechanik Inc, a designerand manufacturer of military optical and electro-opticalsystems, said it received 7.2 mln in contracts from domesticand foreign customers.    Opto Mechanik said the series of contracts included a 3.8mln dlr contract from the U.S. Army Missle Command to producethe sight used to guide the TOW anti-tank missle. Reuter&#3;